You can schedule the app to refresh daily to assure that your app uses up-to-date Salesforce data.

From Setup, enter App Install History, select it, find your app in the list of installed apps, click Schedule, pick days and time for refreshing the app data, then click Save.
title: Schedule Daily Refresh for Salesforce Sales Analytics App
